y recline on their couches!\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":24759,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2017\/05\/03\/prophet-is-a-humble-servant\/","url_meta":{"origin":37122,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Humility: The Prophet is a humble servant","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 3, 2017","format":false,"excerpt":"Yahya ibn Abi Kathir reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cI eat as the servant eats, and I sit as the servant sits. Verily, I am only a servant.\u201d Source: Shu\u2019ab al-Ima\u0304n lil-Bayhaqi\u0304 5572 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u064a\u064e\u062d\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0649 \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0623\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Wisdom \u0627\u0644\u062d\u0643\u0645\u0629","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/wisdom-al-hikmah\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":13623,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2013\/04\/16\/let-not-reject-sunnah\/","url_meta":{"origin":37122,"position":4},"title":"Hadith on Sunnah: Do not reject the Prophet&#8217;s Hadith","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"April 16, 2013","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Raf'i reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cLet me not find one of you reclining on his couch, when a command or prohibition of mine comes to him and he says: I do not know, we only follow what we find in the\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Fai